                        <h4>Key Definitions</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li><b>Velocity:</b> Average monthly sales volume (parsed from CSV).</li>
                            <li><b>Mo. Supply:</b> Estimated months until stock runs out at current velocity.</li>
                            <li><b>On Hand:</b> Total physical units available in the warehouse.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
